            "type": "TextBlock",
            "text": "The Reload's Sunday and Monday deep-dives detailed the rule package — pistol brace repeal, NFA travel relief, FOPA travel clarification, joint NFA applications, electronic 4473s, and more. Acting AG Blanche named ATF Chief Counsel Robert Leider (a former Justice Thomas clerk) as the architect.",
